msgid ""
"Post a job, hire a verified professional or find new work opportunities. "
"Worker Connect brings clients, workers and agents together on one secure "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"Chapisha kazi, ajiri mtaalamu aliyethibitishwa au pata fursa mpya za kazi. "
"Worker Connect inaunganisha wateja, wafanyakazi na mawakala kwenye jukwaa "
"moja salama."

