msgid ""
"Sign in to access your dashboard, manage requests, and connect with workers "
"or clients."
msgstr ""
"Ingia kufikia dashibodi yako, simamia maombi, na kuwasiliana na wafanyakazi "
"au wateja."

msgid ""
"Every worker is ID-verified and approved by our admin team before going live"
msgstr ""
"Kila mfanyakazi anathibitishwa na timu yetu ya utawala kabla ya kuanza kazi"

msgid "Workers clock in and out — clients see progress in real time"
msgstr ""
"Wafanyakazi wanaingia na kutoka — wateja wanaona maendeleo wakati halisi"

msgid "Clients rate workers after each job, building a trusted, safe network"
msgstr ""
"Wateja wanakadiri wafanyakazi baada ya kila kazi, kujenga mtandao wa "
"kuaminiwa na salama"

msgid "Full mobile support — post jobs and manage requests on the go"
msgstr "Msaada kamili wa simu — chapisha kazi na usimamie maombi ukiwa njiani"

msgid ""
"From registration to review, every step is built to protect workers and "
"clients alike."
msgstr ""
"Kuanzia usajili hadi ukaguzi, kila hatua imejengwa kulinda wafanyakazi na "
"wateja."

msgid "Register & Build Your Profile"
msgstr "Jiandikishe na Jenga Wasifu Wako"

msgid ""
"Workers upload their national ID and skills. Clients set up company details."
" Takes just a few minutes to get started."
msgstr ""
"Wafanyakazi wapakua kitambulisho cha taifa na ujuzi. Wateja wanasanidi "
"maelezo ya kampuni. Inachukua dakika chache kuanza."

msgid "Admin Verifies Workers"
msgstr "Wasimamizi Wanathibitisha Wafanyakazi"

msgid ""
"Every worker goes through our review process before appearing as available "
"for hire. No unverified talent on the platform."
msgstr ""
"Kila mfanyakazi anapitia mchakato wetu wa ukaguzi kabla ya kuonekana kama "
"anapatikana kuajiriwa. Hakuna talanta isiyothibitishwa kwenye jukwaa."

msgid "Post a Service Request"
msgstr "Tuma Ombi la Huduma"

msgid ""
"Clients describe the job, choose a category, set the location, date and "
"duration — daily, monthly or custom."
msgstr ""
"Wateja wanaelezea kazi, kuchagua kategoria, kuweka eneo, tarehe na muda — "
"kila siku, kila mwezi au maalum."

msgid "Admin Assigns the Right Worker"
msgstr "Msimamizi Anateua Mfanyakazi Sahihi"

msgid ""
"Our team matches the best verified worker to your request and notifies both "
"parties instantly."
msgstr ""
"Timu yetu inaunganisha mfanyakazi bora aliyethibitishwa na ombi lako na "
"inawaarifu pande zote mara moja."

msgid "Work Tracked Daily"
msgstr "Kazi Inafuatiliwa Kila Siku"

msgid ""
"Assigned workers clock in and out each day. Progress is fully visible to "
"clients and admin at all times."
msgstr ""
"Wafanyakazi waliowekwa wanaingia na kutoka kila siku. Maendeleo yanaonekana "
"kikamilifu kwa wateja na wasimamizi wakati wote."

msgid "Review After Completion"
msgstr "Ukaguzi Baada ya Kukamilika"

msgid ""
"Once the job is done, clients rate the worker. Reviews help surface the best"
" professionals on the platform."
msgstr ""
"Kazi ikisha, wateja wanakadiri mfanyakazi. Ukaguzi husaidia kuonyesha "
"wataalamu bora kwenye jukwaa."

msgid "About Worker Connect"
msgstr "Kuhusu Worker Connect"

msgid "Built for Tanzania's"
msgstr "Imejengwa kwa Tanzania"

msgid "Growing Workforce"
msgstr "Nguvu Kazi Inayokua"

msgid ""
"Worker Connect is Tanzania's first dedicated platform bridging the gap "
"between skilled professionals and the clients who need them — built to solve"
" a real problem with a real digital solution."
msgstr ""
"Worker Connect ni jukwaa la kwanza nchini Tanzania linalounganisha wataalamu"
" wenye ujuzi na wateja wanaowahitaji — limejengwa kutatua tatizo la kweli na"
" suluhisho la kidijitali."

msgid "Fully Verified Network"
msgstr "Mtandao Uliothibitishwa Kikamilifu"

msgid ""
"Every worker is reviewed and approved by admin before going live on the "
"platform."
msgstr ""
"Kila mfanyakazi anakaguliwa na kuidhinishwa na msimamizi kabla ya kuanza "
"kwenye jukwaa."

msgid "Fast Job Matching"
msgstr "Uwianishaji wa Kazi wa Haraka"

msgid ""
"Clients post a job and receive a qualified, verified worker within hours."
msgstr ""
"Wateja wanachapisha kazi na kupata mfanyakazi mwenye sifa na "
"aliyethibitishwa ndani ya masaa machache."

msgid "Agent-Powered Network"
msgstr "Mtandao Unaodhibitiwa na Mawakala"

msgid ""
"Agents recruit and support workers, building stronger local teams across "
"Tanzania."
msgstr ""
"Mawakala wanakusanya na kusaidia wafanyakazi, kujenga timu imara za ndani "
"kote Tanzania."

msgid "Mobile Ready"
msgstr "Tayari kwa Simu"

msgid ""
"Manage jobs, messages and requests from any device, anywhere in Tanzania."
msgstr ""
"Simamia kazi, ujumbe na maombi kutoka kifaa chochote, popote Tanzania."

msgid "Join the Platform"
msgstr "Jiunge na Jukwaa"

msgid "Registered Workers"
msgstr "Wafanyakazi Waliojisajili"

msgid "Client Satisfaction"
msgstr "Kuridhika kwa Wateja"

msgid "Mobile App"
msgstr "Programu ya Simu"

msgid "Take Worker Connect"
msgstr "Chukua Worker Connect"

msgid "Everywhere You Go"
msgstr "Popote Uendapo"

msgid ""
"Manage jobs, track work in real time, receive notifications and communicate "
"with your team — all from your phone. Available free for both workers and "
"clients."
msgstr ""
"Simamia kazi, fuatilia kazi wakati halisi, pokea arifa na wasiliana na timu "
"yako — yote kutoka simu yako. Inapatikana bure kwa wafanyakazi na wateja."

msgid "Download on the"
msgstr "Pakua kwenye"

msgid "App Store"
msgstr "Duka la Programu"

msgid "Get it on"
msgstr "Pata kwenye"

msgid "Google Play"
msgstr "Google Play"

msgid "App coming soon — join the web platform today"
msgstr "Programu inakuja hivi karibuni — jiunge na jukwaa la wavuti leo"

msgid ""
"One platform built for three types of users — each with their own dedicated "
"experience."
msgstr ""
"Jukwaa moja lililojengwa kwa aina tatu za watumiaji — kila mmoja na uzoefu "
"wake maalum."

msgid ""
"Register, upload your documents, get verified by admin and start receiving "
"job assignments from real clients."
msgstr ""
"Jiandikishe, pakia hati zako, thibitishwa na msimamizi na uanze kupokea kazi"
" kutoka kwa wateja wa kweli."

msgid ""
"Post service requests, get matched with a verified worker, and track daily "
"progress — all in one dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Tuma maombi ya huduma, pata mfanyakazi aliyethibitishwa, na ufuatilie "
"maendeleo ya kila siku — yote kwenye dashibodi moja."

msgid ""
"Recruit workers, manage your team, earn commissions and grow your network "
"through the dedicated agent portal."
msgstr ""
"Kusanya wafanyakazi, simamia timu yako, pata kamisheni na ukue mtandao wako "
"kupitia lango la wakala maalum."

msgid ""
"Tanzania's trusted platform connecting clients with verified, skilled "
"professionals for every job — big or small."
msgstr ""
"Jukwaa la kuaminika la Tanzania linalowasiliana wateja na wataalamu wenye "
"ujuzi waliothshibitishwa kwa kila kazi — kubwa au ndogo."

msgid "Platform"
msgstr "Jukwaa"

msgid "Browse Jobs"
msgstr "Angalia Kazi"

msgid "Join As"
msgstr "Jiunge Kama"
